sys_hub_flow.description:
Create a supplier in SAP S4Hana.

Inputs:

  • Supplier Details - Referenced to Supplier Details
  • Account Group - String input needed for SAP S4Hana.

Outputs:

  • Status - Will be set to "1", if the request is "Success" or will be set to "2", if the request is "Error”.
  • Error - Reason for error. opulated only when an error occurs.

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.

Create a supplier in SAP S4Hana.

Inputs:

  • Supplier Details - Referenced to Supplier Details
  • Account Group - String input needed for SAP S4Hana.

Outputs:

  • Status - Will be set to "1", if the request is "Success" or will be set to "2", if the request is "Error”.
  • Error - Reason for error. opulated only when an error occurs.

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.
